##Xiangyang responds to 'rotten vegetables in care' vegetable bag

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zhong Yuhao, reporter, thepaper.cn

In response to a public complaint on March 12 about "rotten vegetables in a caring vegetable bag" received by the Xiangyang 12345 government hotline in Hubei Province, the Commerce Bureau of Fancheng district said on the Xiangyang Government website that the existing problems were known to the government, measures are being taken to further speed up distribution and improve the quality of dishes.

The resident, who said he lived in the home of the four seasons chemical fiber factory on West Daqing Road, Fancheng District, complained: "We received a 17.5 yuan package of caring vegetables, many of which were canola, many of which were rotten, and the distribution of vegetables was uneven and unreasonable. I suggest that you be able to distribute your vegetables properly and pay attention to the inspection."

The Bureau of Commerce of Fancheng district also said in its reply that it would further increase its forces and send the government's concern to thousands of households in a timely manner. "We have instructed the office to rectify the problems you have responded to immediately, " it said.

The paper noted that a number of people have called the 12345 recently to report the "vegetable bag" problem.

Also on March 12, a citizen said, "I am a resident of the Xiuya Garden Community in Hengzhuang. I am also a lonely old man. I ordered 17.5 yuan vegetable bags. The vegetable bags sent to me were Shanghai Green, Cabbage Moss, cabbage and cabbage. Shanghai Green has sent me more than 10 catties. I would suggest more variety."

In response, the Bureau of Agriculture and Rural Affairs of Fancheng district pointed out that according to the requirements of the municipal epidemic prevention headquarters, each vegetable set meal consists of not less than four vegetable combinations, and is mainly made up of local (in the territory of Xiangyang) field bulk vegetables. In Our district, the vegetables in the field are mainly Chinese cabbage, cabbage, Vegetable Moss and Shanghai Green. As the main vegetable collocation, carrots, cauliflower, celery and other seasonal vegetables are less. As a random collocation, they are randomly sent to each office, try to keep each community dish as consistent as possible. Each package of at least 4 varieties of vegetables, not less than 26 Jins for package distribution.

Earlier on March 9, a citizen reported that he was a staff member of Qianzhong road community in Fancheng district. All residents in the district under his jurisdiction had encountered some problems after receiving the vegetable packets issued by the government, residents report that the quality of the vegetables in each bag of vegetables is not consistent, sometimes good and sometimes bad, the quantity of vegetables is more. The residents of the community suggested whether the quantity and quality of vegetables could be reduced.

The fancheng district agricultural and Rural Bureau responded at the time that after picking, transporting, loading and unloading, sorting, weighing, packing, loading, unloading and so on, there was the possibility of less breaking and other phenomena. Due to the temperature during this period, some vegetables stored in plastic bags for a little longer time will also affect its freshness. Special period, please overcome the immediate difficulties of the public, this work more understanding and understanding. Later, we will strengthen supervision and urge relevant units to improve transport efficiency and quality assurance, to avoid similar incidents.

This issue is edited by Xing Tan
